name: Island Siege
description: A fast-paced multiplayer game shooter on Roblox where players work together to defend a crystal on an island against waves of enemies by using various weapons and building defenses.

name: Squirrel Game
description: My submission for my college's game jam. The theme for the game jam is 'every single squirrel'. I created a card game where players can purchase cards and use them to spawn troops. The goal is to use these troops and destroy the enemy AI's base. Please play with full-screen

name: Suprise Discovery
description: A web app for Rose-Hulman students to buy and sell secondhand items with each other.

name: Bartering System IOS
description: An ecommerce IOS mobile application that allow users to post items to sell, or trade items with each other.

name: Exam Review System
description: A web app where Rose-Hulman students can host and join review sessions to study with each other.

name: EventAndPrevent
description: (Note: Use pass for both username and password to log in). This is a web application I made with three other students when I was attending the TechPoint S.O.S challenge. This app calculates new max capacity for convention rooms according to CDC social distancing guidelines and tracked the current capacity of these rooms with respect to their max capacity.
